{"type":"message","id":"b6300f80","parentId":"383702e0","timestamp":"2026-03-11T14:17:56.421Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"session_status-1773238676397963835-53","toolName":"session_status","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.8\n🕒 Time: Wednesday, March 11th, 2026 — 10:17 PM (Asia/Shanghai)\n🧠 Model: custom/gemini-2.5-pro · 🔑 api-key (models.json)\n🧮 Tokens: 9.5k in / 1.7k out · 💵 Cost: $0.0000\n📚 Context: 10k/128k (8%) · 🧹 Compactions: 0\n🧵 Session: agent:main:main • updated just now\n⚙️ Runtime: direct · Think: off · elevated\n🪢 Queue: collect (depth 0)"}],"details":{"ok":true,"sessionKey":"agent:main:main","changedModel":false,"statusText":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.8\n🕒 Time: Wednesday, March 11th, 2026 — 10:17 PM (Asia/Shanghai)\n🧠 Model: custom/gemini-2.5-pro · 🔑 api-key (models.json)\n🧮 Tokens: 9.5k in / 1.7k out · 💵 Cost: $0.0000\n📚 Context: 10k/128k (8%) · 🧹 Compactions: 0\n🧵 Session: agent:main:main • updated just now\n⚙️ Runtime: direct · Think: off · elevated\n🪢 Queue: collect (depth 0)"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773238676419}}
{"type":"message","id":"95135333","parentId":"b6300f80","timestamp":"2026-03-11T14:18:05.656Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老大，我的“大脑”核心驱动模型是 `custom/gemini-2.5-pro`。\n\n您可以把它理解为我用来思考、理解您的话并生成回复的那个核心引擎。\n\n这个模型决定了我处理语言、逻辑推理和创意生成的能力。比如刚才我们聊到的写歌词，就是靠它来完成的。\n\n不过，就像电脑可以换CPU一样，我的模型也是可以根据需要切换的。如果以后有更强或者更适合特定任务的模型，也是可以换上使用的。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-2.5-pro","usage":{"input":143,"output":755,"cacheRead":10206,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":11104,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773238676420}}
