{"type":"message","id":"82781a7b","parentId":"912bf9b4","timestamp":"2026-03-11T14:42:17.090Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about the specific strategies that can be written using Python and pandas in Freqtrade. They want to know what kinds of strategies are possible.\n\nI should search for Freqtrade strategy examples or documentation to provide a comprehensive answer about the types of strategies that can be implemented.\n\nLet me search for Freqtrade strategy examples."},{"type":"text","text":"好的，老大。这个问题很关键！策略是交易机器人的灵魂。 我来搜一下 Freqtrade 官方和社区常用的策略案例，给您列个清单。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8e5bfe3ab4ca4fe8a4e101d4","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"Freqtrade strategy examples python pandas"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"minimax-m2.1","usage":{"input":25987,"output":134,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":26121,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773240132744}}
